{{Top|leg}}
"'''The Ballad of Nomi Sunrider'''" was a song composed by [[Tionne Solusar|Tionne]] in [[11 ABY/Legends|11 ABY]], shortly after the opening of the [[Jedi Praxeum]]. It was composed after weeks of research at the [[Holocron/Legends|Holocron]], and detailed the exploits of [[Nomi Sunrider]] during the [[Great Sith War/Legends|Great Sith War]].

During its first performance, it was interrupted by [[Kyp Durron]], who interjected his own pro-[[Exar Kun/Legends|Exar Kun]] viewpoints.

